en_883680_0	COLOMBO (News 1st) – Dimuth Karunaratne who was arrested for causing an accident while under the influence was released on two sureties of Rs.100,000 each.
en_883680_1	Additional Magistrate Saliya Channa Abeyratne temporarily suspended his driving license.
en_883680_2	The case was postponed to May 2nd.
en_883680_3	Dimuth Karunaratne, addressed social media and apologized for his actions and said he was well aware that it was ‘utterly unbecoming of a Sri Lankan National Cricketer and apologized to the owner of the three-wheeler and driver who sustained minor injuries.
en_883680_4	His statement stressed he had followed the due legal process and had abided by all formalities therein required.
en_883680_5	He also promised to assist with whatever legal obligations necessary from his end.
